(120, 29, 'multiedit_OrangeSection', '<p>CSPNetworks solves unique technology challenges by developing and implementing cost-effective, scalable solutions that are guaranteed to work. We continue the relationship by maintaining it through our suite of value added services.&nbsp;</p>'),
(121, 29, 'multiedit_GreenSection', '<p>CSPBackup is built for businesses who understand and require a solid data protection solution that is supported locally and backed by an experienced team of system engineers who are able to recover your data when you need it most.</p>'),
(122, 29, 'multiedit_BlueSection', '<p>CSPCloud provides end-to-end managed hosting solutions. From domain registration to dedicated servers to email and collaboration services, our clients count on us daily to deliver the essential cloud services for their business.</p>'),
